<h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Application</h1>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Personal details</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">Provide some basic details about yourself, like how to contact you about this application.</p>

<div class="govuk-form-group"><label for="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-first-name-field" class="govuk-label govuk-label--s">First name</label><input id="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-first-name-field" class="govuk-input govuk-!-width-one-half" aria-required="true" type="text" name="jobseekers_job_application_personal_details_form[first_name]"></div>

<div class="govuk-form-group"><label for="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-last-name-field" class="govuk-label govuk-label--s">Last name</label><input id="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-last-name-field" class="govuk-input govuk-!-width-one-half" aria-required="true" type="text" name="jobseekers_job_application_personal_details_form[last_name]"></div>

<div class="govuk-form-group"><label for="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-phone-number-field" class="govuk-label govuk-label--s">Phone number</label><div class="govuk-hint" id="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-phone-number-hint">Enter a phone number you are happy to be contacted on. For example, 01632 960 001, 07700 900 982 or +44 0808 157 0192.</div><input id="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-phone-number-field" class="govuk-input govuk-!-width-one-half" aria-describedby="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-phone-number-hint" aria-required="true" type="tel" name="jobseekers_job_application_personal_details_form[phone_number]"></div>

<div class="govuk-form-group"><label for="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-email-address-field" class="govuk-label govuk-label--s">Email address</label><input id="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-email-address-field" class="govuk-input govuk-!-width-one-half" aria-required="true" value="halima.ikuomola@education.gov.uk" type="email" name="jobseekers_job_application_personal_details_form[email_address]"></div>
    
<div class="govuk-form-group"><fieldset class="govuk-fieldset" aria-describedby="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-right-to-work-in-uk-hint"><legend class="govuk-fieldset__legend govuk-fieldset__legend--s"><h3 class="govuk-fieldset__heading">Do you need Skilled Worker visa sponsorship?</h3></legend><div class="govuk-hint" id="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-right-to-work-in-uk-hint">You can <a class="govuk-link" target="_blank" href="https://getintoteaching.education.gov.uk/non-uk-teachers/teach-in-england-if-you-trained-overseas#apply-for-your-visa">find out what visa you need if you're a non-UK citizen (link opens in new tab).</a></div><div class="govuk-radios" data-module="govuk-radios" data-govuk-radios-init=""><div class="govuk-radios__item"><input id="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-right-to-work-in-uk-yes-field" class="govuk-radios__input" type="radio" value="yes" name="jobseekers_job_application_personal_details_form[right_to_work_in_uk]"><label for="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-right-to-work-in-uk-yes-field" class="govuk-label govuk-radios__label">No, I already have the right to work in the UK</label></div><div class="govuk-radios__item"><input id="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-right-to-work-in-uk-no-field" class="govuk-radios__input" type="radio" value="no" name="jobseekers_job_application_personal_details_form[right_to_work_in_uk]" aria-controls="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-right-to-work-in-uk-no-conditional" aria-expanded="false"><label for="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-right-to-work-in-uk-no-field" class="govuk-label govuk-radios__label">Yes, I will need to apply for a visa giving me the right to work in the UK</label></div><div class="govuk-radios__conditional govuk-radios__conditional--hidden" id="jobseekers-job-application-personal-details-form-right-to-work-in-uk-no-conditional"><div class="govuk-warning-text"><span class="govuk-warning-text__icon" aria-hidden="true">!</span><strong class="govuk-warning-text__text"><span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Warning</span>This role cannot offer visa sponsorship.</strong></div><p class="govuk-body">It is unlikely you will be considered for this job as it is not offering Skilled Worker visa sponsorship to non-UK citizens.</p><p class="govuk-body">Learn more about <a class="govuk-link" target="_blank" href="https://getintoteaching.education.gov.uk/non-uk-teachers/teach-in-england-if-you-trained-overseas#apply-for-your-visa">teaching in England as a non-UK citizen (opens in new tab).</a></p><a class="govuk-button govuk-button--secondary" href="/jobs">Search for other jobs</a></div></div></fieldset></div>

<fieldset class="govuk-fieldset" aria-describedby="jobseekers-job-application-professional-status-form-has-teacher-reference-number-hint"><legend class="govuk-fieldset__legend govuk-fieldset__legend--s"><h3 class="govuk-fieldset__heading">Do you have a teacher reference number (TRN)?</h3></legend><div class="govuk-hint" id="jobseekers-job-application-professional-status-form-has-teacher-reference-number-hint"><p>Schools will only be able to see your TRN if you apply for a role. You can <a class="govuk-link" target="_blank" href="https://find-a-lost-trn.education.gov.uk/start">find your TRN</a> if you do not know it (for example, if you're a trainee teacher) or have forgotten it. Your TRN is 7 digits long.</p></div><div class="govuk-radios" data-module="govuk-radios" data-govuk-radios-init=""><div class="govuk-radios__item"><input id="jobseekers-job-application-professional-status-form-has-teacher-reference-number-yes-field" class="govuk-radios__input" type="radio" value="yes" checked="checked" name="jobseekers_job_application_professional_status_form[has_teacher_reference_number]" aria-controls="jobseekers-job-application-professional-status-form-has-teacher-reference-number-yes-conditional" aria-expanded="false"><label for="jobseekers-job-application-professional-status-form-has-teacher-reference-number-yes-field" class="govuk-label govuk-radios__label">Yes</label></div><div class="govuk-radios__conditional govuk-radios__conditional--hidden" id="jobseekers-job-application-professional-status-form-has-teacher-reference-number-yes-conditional"><div class="govuk-form-group"><label for="jobseekers-job-application-professional-status-form-teacher-reference-number-field" class="govuk-label">What is your teacher reference number (TRN)?</label><input id="jobseekers-job-application-professional-status-form-teacher-reference-number-field" class="govuk-input" type="text" value="1212121" name="jobseekers_job_application_professional_status_form[teacher_reference_number]"></div></div><div class="govuk-radios__item"><input id="jobseekers-job-application-professional-status-form-has-teacher-reference-number-no-field" class="govuk-radios__input" type="radio" value="no" name="jobseekers_job_application_professional_status_form[has_teacher_reference_number]"><label for="jobseekers-job-application-professional-status-form-has-teacher-reference-number-no-field" class="govuk-label govuk-radios__label">No</label></div></div></fieldset>
